{"tid":1389330,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"除咗捐飯券仲可以點幫...","createTime":"2019-07-31T01:21:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T02:35:22.000Z","uid":190579,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7927dbe0586297aa417dd5d2c5f7113657cc6e34","tid":1389330,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:21:11.000Z","msg":"見到義士比狗拉、比狗打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我放低唔到自己既包袱，冇勇氣去現場幫佢地，真係極之極之內疚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前有捐過裝備，送過飯券，籌過旗登報。<br />\n但擺低錢之後，我唔覺得我改變咗D乜野，前線依然比狗打到仆街，拉到仆街，我依然覺得好無力好自責。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔想佢地再咁樣落去，最後死既死，傷既傷，坐監既坐監。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地咁固執死守街頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，係因為佢地見唔到除此以外仲有咩出路<br />\n<br />\n我一個和理非，可以最大程度幫到佢地，令佢地唔好再自殘同送死既方法﹐就係<span style=\"color: red;\">罷工</span>，同埋說服朋友同事罷工，仲有就係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>說服你班連登仔罷工</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我要話比佢地知，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">和理非都可以做到野</span></strong>，你地休息一下，等和理非出手！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非們！我地一齊<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">８月５起無限期罷工</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">接前線力，比佢地唞唞！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tmWFJ2z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtmWFJ2z.jpg&h=2d73a0ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QfZghnz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQfZghnz.jpg&h=850e398c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qznEZAV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqznEZAV.jpg&h=309f0d76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OirN8uf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOirN8uf.jpg&h=502ee781&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"973cba491d77a787da4b23857e5e55bff6614e06","tid":1389330,"uid":190579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:21:25.000Z","msg":"85我罷工"},{"pid":"297ea9f84b81c2021f50abcd5a0741978dd89793","tid":1389330,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:22:08.000Z","msg":"85我罷工"},{"pid":"3b34ee67d2387cc611db21e00a74573bdf3be9f2","tid":1389330,"uid":254484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:22:08.000Z","msg":"我都想捐"},{"pid":"d48d91af6d1b6348ec9db8b329439eb0845d9816","tid":1389330,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b34ee67d2387cc611db21e00a74573bdf3be9f2","tid":1389330,"uid":254484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:22:08.000Z","msg":"我都想捐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:23:43.000Z","msg":"罷工啦<br />\n唉...我發現佢地大部分根本唔想收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，佢地有家教有自尊，我都唔知講咩好<br />\n唯有自己做D野，希望佢地唔使再走上街頭"},{"pid":"0fa6aa4318414e9fb5d24f70359698184aed34d4","tid":1389330,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited